- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper mentions the row space of the input matrix, which is a concept related to control theory. 
- cs.DS (Dynamical Systems) is a possibility as the paper deals with the computation of matrices, which can be used to represent dynamical systems. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a possibility as the paper mentions the Popov form, which is a concept related to computational geometry. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possibility as the paper deals with the computation of systems of equations, which is a topic related to logic in computer science.
